{"tid":1995920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得土盟吳卓恆好勁？","createTime":"2020-04-30T15:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T22:54:36.000Z","uid":66987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca1f47de8c5a5bd52c104902db7ceccaa045f15","tid":1995920,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"(之前有條仆街用左我連登專登寫D借刀post插恆仔，呢度真係好抱歉)<br />\n澄清文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1995142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1995142</a> <br />\n佢真係好好心機喺medium同土盟寫關於反對迫遷嘅呼籲<br />\n仲有基進報導其實係佢搞嘅<br />\n但係一直都冇乜人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且佢又靚仔<br />\n又好心機去寫文<br />\n個人覺得佢D文章真係寫好好<br />\n值得一讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢medium:<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@ngcheukhang22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40ngcheukhang22&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=600de521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@ngcheukhang22</a>"},{"pid":"a4aeee3c838e7beafbdd27ae9ec96bddaac80889","tid":1995920,"uid":66987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/1946/45407527931_5c5a95bee6_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F1946%2F45407527931_5c5a95bee6_b.jpg&h=b8cf1e28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cde887addb22107fedd7ba60afc0985672e24a63","tid":1995920,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e194828b61281d8b223339fd82305f61a97a9a4","tid":1995920,"